export type _EuiThemeBase = number;

export const EuiThemeSizes = [
  'xxs',
  'xs',
  's',
  'm',
  'base',
  'l',
  'xl',
  'xxl',
  'xxxl',

export type _EuiThemeSize = typeof EuiThemeSizes[number];
